You know Ira James,

01:07.317 --> 01:09.277
right?

01:09.319 --> 01:11.989
All-state fullback, state

01:09.319 --> 01:11.989
single season rushing record.

01:12.031 --> 01:14.825
Who am I kidding? He's probably

01:12.031 --> 01:14.825
never even talked to you.

