But now, after ten

18:53.382 --> 18:55.802
days on your own, you...

18:55.843 --> 18:58.178
you're a functioning

18:55.843 --> 18:58.178
member of society.

18:58.220 --> 18:59.179
Wow!

18:59.221 --> 19:01.766
I must have

18:59.221 --> 19:01.766
really changed.

