Mail call!

19:07.271 --> 19:08.856
I confiscated your Victoria's

19:07.271 --> 19:08.856
Secret catalog.

19:08.898 --> 19:11.484
A kid your age should...

19:08.898 --> 19:11.484
Oh, you're entertaining.

