19:30.711 --> 19:32.379
activate it.

19:32.421 --> 19:34.048
"Two-four-seven-one."

19:34.090 --> 19:36.592
Now, listen, I already

19:34.090 --> 19:36.592
transferred a $3,000 balance

19:36.634 --> 19:38.218
from the Valley

19:36.634 --> 19:38.218
Federal Card

19:38.260 --> 19:40.013
over to my Spring

19:38.260 --> 19:40.013
Mills Mutual Card,

19:40.054 --> 19:41.430
because I had

19:40.054 --> 19:41.430
an $8,000 limit.

19:41.472 --> 19:43.599
But since I'm already

19:41.472 --> 19:43.599
bumping against that,

19:43.641 --> 19:46.144
I might as well transfer

19:43.641 --> 19:46.144
everything to yours,

19:46.185 --> 19:47.603
because it has

19:46.185 --> 19:47.603
a $20,000 limit.

19:47.645 --> 19:49.814
Sure, I'd love to

19:47.645 --> 19:49.814
talk to a supervisor.

19:49.856 --> 19:51.231
Hey! I was on the phone!

19:51.273 --> 19:52.399
You've been using credit cards?

19:52.441 --> 19:53.818
How much have you spent?

19:53.860 --> 19:55.235
Ten, 11 grand.

19:55.277 --> 19:56.154
But I'm still

19:56.195 --> 19:57.237
way under the $20,000 limit.

19:57.279 --> 19:59.406
How can you spend

19:57.279 --> 19:59.406
that much in ten days?

19:59.448 --> 20:01.617
Well, you know,

19:59.448 --> 20:01.617
I got that new convection oven,

20:01.659 --> 20:04.244
and that made the refrigerator

20:01.659 --> 20:04.244
look kind of shabby.

20:04.286 --> 20:06.039
Plus, I had to buy new clothes

20:06.080 --> 20:07.165
every time mine got dirty.

20:07.206 --> 20:08.415
And that giant gong

20:07.206 --> 20:08.415
in the bathroom?

20:08.457 --> 20:10.292
I mean,

20:08.457 --> 20:10.292
how do you guys do it?

20:10.334 --> 20:13.253
Ow! Ow! Ow! Ow!

20:13.295 --> 20:14.463
Reese, I really owe

20:13.295 --> 20:14.463
you some thanks

20:14.505 --> 20:16.049
for giving me some

20:14.505 --> 20:16.049
faith in myself.

20:16.090 --> 20:18.843
The next few days, I will

20:16.090 --> 20:18.843
be saying very little.

20:18.885 --> 20:20.928
I will be deciding

20:18.885 --> 20:20.928
on a punishment.

20:20.970 --> 20:22.972
Ideas are already

20:20.970 --> 20:22.972
popping into my mind.

20:23.014 --> 20:25.850
It's really very exciting,

20:23.014 --> 20:25.850
but I don't want to get hasty

20:25.892 --> 20:27.894
and leave either of us

20:25.892 --> 20:27.894
feeling dissatisfied.

