Ow! You're going to drag me

20:27.935 --> 20:30.270
all the way home?

20:30.312 --> 20:31.981
Well, we're taking

20:30.312 --> 20:31.981
your ear there.

20:32.023 --> 20:35.068
If the rest of you wants

20:32.023 --> 20:35.068
to come, that's fine, too.

20:35.109 --> 20:37.653
It's been almost a month,

20:35.109 --> 20:37.653
and Mom's still coming up

20:37.695 --> 20:39.279
with fresh punishments

20:37.695 --> 20:39.279
for Reese.

20:39.321 --> 20:41.281
She says she's never felt

20:39.321 --> 20:41.281
more creative.

20:41.323 --> 20:43.201
She must be doing

20:41.323 --> 20:43.201
something right.

20:43.242 --> 20:44.911
He has a white streak

20:43.242 --> 20:44.911
in his hair.

20:44.952 --> 20:45.870
Hey, Malcolm. Guess what.

20:45.912 --> 20:47.496
I got accepted.

20:45.912 --> 20:47.496
I'm going to college.

20:47.538 --> 20:48.956
Really? Which school?

20:48.998 --> 20:51.792
All of them--

20:48.998 --> 20:51.792
A&M, Tulane, Georgia, Stanford.

20:51.834 --> 20:54.294
Full scholarships

20:51.834 --> 20:54.294
and everything.

20:54.336 --> 20:56.214
Stanford liked your essay?

20:56.255 --> 20:59.008
No, I forgot to put it in

20:56.255 --> 20:59.008
the envelope. I got in, anyway.

20:59.050 --> 21:01.010
But don't worry.

20:59.050 --> 21:01.010
That essay didn't go to waste.

21:01.052 --> 21:04.013
I handed it in as

21:01.052 --> 21:04.013
my math midterm and got an "A."

21:04.055 --> 21:06.224
Thanks for making me believe

21:04.055 --> 21:06.224
in myself, Malcolm.

21:06.265 --> 21:08.935
You proved that I don't need

21:06.265 --> 21:08.935
all these people helping me.

21:08.976 --> 21:10.644
See ya.

21:11.395 --> 21:13.814
Stanford. Poor guy.

21:13.856 --> 21:15.691
I'll bet he doesn't know

21:13.856 --> 21:15.691
it only has

21:15.733 --> 21:18.318
the third-best astrophysics

21:15.733 --> 21:18.318
department in the country.
